      <p
        begin="00:15:07.491"
        end="00:15:12.412"><span region="Default">It is such an honor<br/>to get to say these words to you.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:13.580"
        end="00:15:17.584"><span region="Default">Vancouver, welcome to The Eras Tour!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:17.668"
        end="00:15:19.670"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:27.386"
        end="00:15:28.637"><span region="Default">You know we have, uh...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:29.888"
        end="00:15:33.100"><span region="Default">we have toured the entire world<br/>with this tour.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:33.183"
        end="00:15:34.893"><span region="Default">We have had so many adventures,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:34.977"
        end="00:15:38.564"><span region="Default">it has been the most exciting,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:38.647"
        end="00:15:43.235"><span region="Default">powerful, electrifying, intense,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:43.944"
        end="00:15:47.447"><span region="Default">most challenging thing<br/>I've ever done in my entire life.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:47.531"
        end="00:15:53.078"><span region="Default">We've gotten to perform<br/>for over ten million people on this tour.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:53.161"
        end="00:15:55.163"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:15:58.250"
        end="00:15:59.251"><span region="Default">And tonight...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:00.002"
        end="00:16:05.048"><span region="Default">we get to play one last show for you<br/>here tonight in beautiful Vancouver.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:16.685"
        end="00:16:21.732"><span region="Default">So you and I, we're about to go on<br/>one last grand adventure together,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:21.815"
        end="00:16:26.236"><span region="Default">and that adventure is gonna<br/>span 18 years of music.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:26.320"
        end="00:16:29.448"><span region="Default">And we're gonna be doing this<br/>one era at a time.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:29.531"
        end="00:16:31.325"><span region="Default">How does that sound to you, Vancouver?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:31.408"
        end="00:16:33.410"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:37.456"
        end="00:16:38.957"><span region="Default">Okay, so here's something you should know.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:39.041"
        end="00:16:40.876"><span region="Default">You're about to hear a lot of songs.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:40.959"
        end="00:16:42.920"><span region="Default">There are a lot of songs in this show,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:43.003"
        end="00:16:46.006"><span region="Default">and these are songs I either wrote<br/>about something that happened in my life,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:46.089"
        end="00:16:47.674"><span region="Default">a feeling I felt at one point</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:47.758"
        end="00:16:50.636"><span region="Default">or maybe something<br/>I just invented in my imagination.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:50.719"
        end="00:16:52.429"><span region="Default">And maybe that's what you think about</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:52.513"
        end="00:16:54.348"><span region="Default">when you hear these songs<br/>playing out in the world.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:55.182"
        end="00:16:57.059"><span region="Default">But all that's about to change<br/>after tonight,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:16:57.142"
        end="00:17:00.270"><span region="Default">because after tonight,<br/>when you hear these songs,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:00.354"
        end="00:17:03.273"><span region="Default">you're gonna think about us<br/>and the memories we made here tonight</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:03.357"
        end="00:17:04.566"><span region="Default">on The Eras Tour!</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:04.650"
        end="00:17:06.235"><span region="Default">I'll be your host this evening.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:17:07.027"
        end="00:17:08.070"><span region="Default">My name is Taylor.</span></p>
