        begin="00:44:02.851"
        end="00:44:05.687"><span region="Default">[chorus]<br/>♪ Flew me to places I'd never been ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:05.771"
        end="00:44:09.691"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, now I'm lying<br/>on the cold hard ground! ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:09.775"
        end="00:44:12.277"><span region="Default">[chorus] ♪ Oh, oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:12.361"
        end="00:44:14.112"><span region="Default">-♪ Hey ♪<br/>-[chorus] ♪ Trouble, trouble, trouble ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:14.196"
