        begin="00:44:15.989"
        end="00:44:18.492"><span region="Default">[chorus] ♪ Oh, oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:18.575"
        end="00:44:21.203"><span region="Default">♪ Trouble, trouble, trouble ♪</span></p>
