      <p
        begin="00:44:25.123"
        end="00:44:27.417"><span region="Default">♪ Trouble, trouble, trouble ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:27.501"
        end="00:44:31.296"><span region="Default">[chorus] ♪ I knew you were trouble<br/>when you walked in ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:31.380"
        end="00:44:33.799"><span region="Default">♪ Trouble, trouble, trouble ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:44:33.882"
        end="00:44:36.677"><span region="Default">-[♪ song ends]<br/>-[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:15.424"
        end="00:45:17.968"><span region="Default">How are we liking the Red Era so far,<br/>Vancouver?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:18.051"
        end="00:45:19.720"><span region="Default">[cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:24.308"
        end="00:45:26.643"><span region="Default">You know this, this tour has been, uh...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:26.727"
        end="00:45:29.730"><span region="Default">it's been different from any tour<br/>I've ever done before</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:30.606"
        end="00:45:33.233"><span region="Default">in so many ways I can't count,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:34.026"
        end="00:45:35.944"><span region="Default">but I'd like to tell you a few, um...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:37.362"
        end="00:45:39.948"><span region="Default">I've been touring since<br/>I was 15 years old and, um,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:41.158"
        end="00:45:43.243"><span region="Default">basically what I would do<br/>in the beginning.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:43.327"
        end="00:45:46.830"><span region="Default">First of all, I opened up for so many<br/>artists for a couple of years</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:46.914"
        end="00:45:50.375"><span region="Default">and then when I was lucky enough to start<br/>going on my own headlining tours,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:50.459"
        end="00:45:53.212"><span region="Default">I would make an album<br/>and then I would go on tour</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:53.295"
        end="00:45:55.088"><span region="Default">and the tour would be named<br/>after that album.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:55.172"
        end="00:45:56.590"><span region="Default">So, you know, you do The Fearless Tour,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:45:56.673"
        end="00:45:59.635"><span region="Default">the Speak Now Tour, the Red Tour,<br/>1989, Reputation,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:00.177"
        end="00:46:01.386"><span region="Default">you, you... [chuckles]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:01.470"
        end="00:46:05.682"><span region="Default">...basically kinda follow the same formula<br/>for a long time.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:05.766"
        end="00:46:06.850"><span region="Default">And, um...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:08.101"
        end="00:46:09.436"><span region="Default">and then, uh...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:10.020"
        end="00:46:14.441"><span region="Default">I ended up putting out so much music,<br/>so quickly that,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:15.651"
        end="00:46:18.529"><span region="Default">that basically I had to kind of<br/>think of a new way to do it.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:18.612"
        end="00:46:21.823"><span region="Default">And, um, I really hoped that<br/>it was something you would like,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:21.907"
        end="00:46:24.993"><span region="Default">and, uh, I came up with this idea<br/>called The Eras Tour.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:25.077"
        end="00:46:27.246"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:30.290"
        end="00:46:33.460"><span region="Default">And then the craziest thing<br/>about this has been</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:33.544"
        end="00:46:35.712"><span region="Default">and the reason this has been<br/>the longest tour I've ever done,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:35.796"
        end="00:46:38.549"><span region="Default">I've never, ever done<br/>this many shows on a tour ever,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:39.132"
        end="00:46:41.718"><span region="Default">uh, is because you guys have made this</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:41.802"
        end="00:46:46.098"><span region="Default">into something completely unrecognizable<br/>from anything I've ever done in my life.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:46.181"
        end="00:46:49.142"><span region="Default">With your traditions, with your,<br/>your passion, with your--</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:49.226"
        end="00:46:53.105"><span region="Default">The way you care about this tour,<br/>it's, it's unparalleled.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:53.188"
        end="00:46:55.357"><span region="Default">I've never experienced anything like it.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:55.858"
        end="00:46:59.278"><span region="Default">And, you know,<br/>I never thought that</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:46:59.361"
        end="00:47:01.530"><span region="Default">writing one line<br/>about friendship bracelets</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:01.613"
        end="00:47:05.784"><span region="Default">would have you guys all making<br/>thousands of friendship bracelets.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:08.203"
        end="00:47:11.123"><span region="Default">And making friends<br/>and just bringing joy to each other,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:11.206"
        end="00:47:14.334"><span region="Default">um, that is,<br/>I think the lasting legacy of this tour</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:14.418"
        end="00:47:17.838"><span region="Default">is the fact that you have created<br/>such a space of joy</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:17.921"
        end="00:47:23.677"><span region="Default">and, um, and togetherness and... love.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:23.760"
        end="00:47:27.764"><span region="Default">I can't be-- I couldn't be<br/>more proud of you, honestly,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:27.848"
        end="00:47:29.683"><span region="Default">That, that is all you.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:29.766"
        end="00:47:32.060"><span region="Default">That's what people think about<br/>when they think about this tour</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:32.144"
        end="00:47:34.188"><span region="Default">is how they felt<br/>out in the crowd with you.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:34.771"
        end="00:47:38.859"><span region="Default">So, I just wanted to say that that<br/>you're why this is so special.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:38.942"
        end="00:47:42.070"><span region="Default">And you supporting me<br/>for as long as you have</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:42.154"
        end="00:47:47.784"><span region="Default">is why I get to take these lovely walks<br/>down memory lane every single night</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:47.868"
        end="00:47:50.579"><span region="Default">because you've cared about every era</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:50.662"
        end="00:47:53.749"><span region="Default">of my entire life<br/>that I've been making music.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:53.832"
        end="00:47:56.043"><span region="Default">So, thank you for that.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:47:56.126"
        end="00:47:57.753"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:00.255"
        end="00:48:01.381"><span region="Default">There's actually a...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:02.257"
        end="00:48:04.510"><span region="Default">There's one more song from Red<br/>that I'd love to play for you</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:04.593"
        end="00:48:08.055"><span region="Default">if you happen to have<br/>10 minutes to spare.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:08.138"
        end="00:48:09.556"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:12.351"
        end="00:48:15.187"><span region="Default">[♪ "All Too Well (10 Minute Version)"<br/>playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:33.205"
        end="00:48:36.250"><span region="Default">♪ I walked through<br/>the door with you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:36.333"
        end="00:48:38.293"><span region="Default">♪ The air was cold ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:38.377"
        end="00:48:42.464"><span region="Default">♪ But something 'bout it<br/>felt like home somehow ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:42.548"
        end="00:48:47.803"><span region="Default">♪ And I left my scarf there<br/>at your sister's house ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:48:47.886"
        end="00:48:53.767"><span region="Default">♪ And you've still got it<br/>in your drawer, even now ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:03.652"
        end="00:49:09.199"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, your sweet disposition<br/>and my wide-eyed gaze ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:09.283"
        end="00:49:13.829"><span region="Default">♪ We're singing in the car<br/>Getting lost upstate ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:14.663"
        end="00:49:18.834"><span region="Default">♪ Autumn leaves falling down<br/>like pieces into place ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:18.917"
        end="00:49:24.256"><span region="Default">♪ And I can picture it<br/>after all these days ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:24.339"
        end="00:49:27.217"><span region="Default">♪ And I know it's long gone and ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:27.301"
        end="00:49:29.970"><span region="Default">♪ That magic's not here no more ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:30.053"
        end="00:49:31.722"><span region="Default">♪ And I might be okay ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:31.805"
        end="00:49:35.100"><span region="Default">♪ But I'm not fine at all ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:35.184"
        end="00:49:39.771"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, oh, oh ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:40.480"
        end="00:49:45.068"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause there we are again<br/>on that little town street ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:45.152"
        end="00:49:47.237"><span region="Default">♪ You almost ran the red ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:47.321"
        end="00:49:49.823"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause you were lookin' over at me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:49.907"
        end="00:49:52.451"><span region="Default">♪ Wind in my hair, I was there ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:49:52.534"
        end="00:49:58.207"><span region="Default">♪ I remember it all too well ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:00.501"
        end="00:50:05.464"><span region="Default">♪ Photo album on the counter<br/>Your cheeks were turning red ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:05.547"
        end="00:50:07.174"><span region="Default">♪ You used to be a little kid ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:07.257"
        end="00:50:10.969"><span region="Default">♪ With glasses in a twin-sized bed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:11.053"
        end="00:50:14.014"><span region="Default">♪ Your mother's telling<br/>stories 'bout you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:14.097"
        end="00:50:15.891"><span region="Default">♪ On the tee-ball team ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:16.475"
        end="00:50:18.227"><span region="Default">♪ You told me 'bout your past ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:18.310"
        end="00:50:20.896"><span region="Default">♪ Thinking your future was me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:20.979"
        end="00:50:23.482"><span region="Default">♪ And you were tossing me the car keys ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:23.565"
        end="00:50:25.609"><span region="Default">♪ "Fuck the patriarchy" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:25.692"
        end="00:50:27.653"><span region="Default">♪ Keychain on the ground ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:27.736"
        end="00:50:31.031"><span region="Default">♪ We were always skipping town ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:31.114"
        end="00:50:34.034"><span region="Default">♪ And I was thinking on the drive down ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:34.117"
        end="00:50:37.955"><span region="Default">♪ Any time now<br/>He's gonna say it's love ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:38.038"
        end="00:50:40.582"><span region="Default">♪ You never called it what it was ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:41.416"
        end="00:50:44.336"><span region="Default">♪ Till we were dead and gone and buried ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:44.419"
        end="00:50:46.296"><span region="Default">♪ Check the pulse and come back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:46.380"
        end="00:50:48.340"><span region="Default">♪ Swearing it's the same ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:48.423"
        end="00:50:51.009"><span region="Default">♪ After three months in the grave ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:51.885"
        end="00:50:54.721"><span region="Default">♪ And then you wondered where it went to ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:54.805"
        end="00:50:56.390"><span region="Default">♪ As I reached for you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:56.473"
        end="00:50:58.600"><span region="Default">♪ But all I felt was shame ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:50:58.684"
        end="00:51:02.271"><span region="Default">♪ And you held my lifeless frame ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:02.354"
        end="00:51:05.274"><span region="Default">♪ And I know it's long gone and ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:05.357"
        end="00:51:07.693"><span region="Default">♪ There was nothing else I could do ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:07.776"
        end="00:51:10.445"><span region="Default">♪ And I forget about you long enough ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:10.529"
        end="00:51:17.160"><span region="Default">♪ To forget why I needed to ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:18.370"
        end="00:51:22.833"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause there we are again<br/>in the middle of the night ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:23.667"
        end="00:51:25.377"><span region="Default">♪ We're dancing 'round the kitchen ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:25.460"
        end="00:51:27.921"><span region="Default">♪ In the refrigerator light ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:28.005"
        end="00:51:30.507"><span region="Default">♪ Down the stairs, I was there ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:30.591"
        end="00:51:37.347"><span region="Default">♪ I remember it all too well ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:39.057"
        end="00:51:43.645"><span region="Default">♪ And there we are again<br/>when nobody had to know ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:44.396"
        end="00:51:48.525"><span region="Default">♪ You kept me like a secret<br/>but I kept you like an oath ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:48.609"
        end="00:51:51.153"><span region="Default">♪ Sacred prayer and we'd swear ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:51.236"
        end="00:51:53.113"><span region="Default">♪ To remember it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:51:53.197"
        end="00:51:59.912"><span region="Default">♪ All too well, yeah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:03.832"
        end="00:52:06.001"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:14.176"
        end="00:52:17.262"><span region="Default">♪ Well, maybe we got lost in translation ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:17.346"
        end="00:52:19.598"><span region="Default">♪ Maybe I asked for too much ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:19.681"
        end="00:52:22.518"><span region="Default">♪ But maybe this thing was a masterpiece ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:22.601"
        end="00:52:24.353"><span region="Default">♪ Till you tore it all up ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:24.436"
        end="00:52:27.147"><span region="Default">♪ Running scared, I was there ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:27.231"
        end="00:52:34.196"><span region="Default">♪ I remember it all too well ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:35.155"
        end="00:52:37.741"><span region="Default">♪ And you call me up again ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:37.824"
        end="00:52:40.661"><span region="Default">♪ Just to break me like a promise ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:40.744"
        end="00:52:45.332"><span region="Default">♪ So casually cruel in<br/>the name of "being honest" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:45.415"
        end="00:52:49.503"><span region="Default">♪ I'm a crumpled up<br/>piece of paper lying here ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:49.586"
        end="00:52:56.009"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I remember it all, all, all ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:56.093"
        end="00:52:58.929"><span region="Default">♪ They say all's well that ends well ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:52:59.012"
        end="00:53:00.973"><span region="Default">♪ But I'm in a new hell ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:01.056"
        end="00:53:06.353"><span region="Default">♪ Every time you double-cross my mind ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:06.436"
        end="00:53:10.065"><span region="Default">♪ You said if we had been closer in age ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:10.148"
        end="00:53:13.527"><span region="Default">♪ Maybe it would have been fine ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:13.610"
        end="00:53:16.947"><span region="Default">♪ And that made me want to die ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:17.030"
        end="00:53:19.783"><span region="Default">♪ The idea you had of me<br/>Who was she? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:19.867"
        end="00:53:23.287"><span region="Default">♪ A never-needy ever-lovely jewel ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:23.370"
        end="00:53:27.082"><span region="Default">♪ Whose shine reflects on you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:27.165"
        end="00:53:29.710"><span region="Default">♪ Not weeping in a party bathroom ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:29.793"
        end="00:53:33.463"><span region="Default">♪ Some actress asking me<br/>what happened, you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:34.173"
        end="00:53:37.467"><span region="Default">♪ That's what happened, you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:37.551"
        end="00:53:42.764"><span region="Default">♪ You who charmed my dad<br/>with self-effacing jokes ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:42.848"
        end="00:53:47.436"><span region="Default">♪ Sipping coffee like<br/>you're on a late-night show ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:47.519"
        end="00:53:50.731"><span region="Default">♪ But then he watched me watch<br/>the front door all night ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:50.814"
        end="00:53:52.441"><span region="Default">♪ Willing you to come ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:52.524"
        end="00:53:55.903"><span region="Default">♪ And he said<br/>"It's supposed to be fun ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:53:55.986"
        end="00:53:58.906"><span region="Default">♪ "Turning twenty-one" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:00.240"
        end="00:54:02.284"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:11.502"
        end="00:54:13.086"><span region="Default">♪ Time won't fly ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:13.170"
        end="00:54:16.131"><span region="Default">♪ It's like I'm paralyzed by it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:16.215"
        end="00:54:18.800"><span region="Default">♪ I'd like to be my old self again ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:18.884"
        end="00:54:21.220"><span region="Default">♪ But I'm still trying to find it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:21.303"
        end="00:54:23.430"><span region="Default">♪ After plaid shirt days ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:23.514"
        end="00:54:26.642"><span region="Default">♪ And nights when you made me your own ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:26.725"
        end="00:54:31.855"><span region="Default">♪ Now you mail back my things<br/>and I walk home alone ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:31.939"
        end="00:54:36.860"><span region="Default">♪ But you keep my old scarf<br/>from that very first week ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:36.944"
        end="00:54:39.279"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause it reminds you of innocence ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:39.363"
        end="00:54:41.657"><span region="Default">♪ And it smells like me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="00:54:41.740"
