        end="01:24:38.954"><span region="Default">♪ You put me on<br/>And said I was your favorite ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:54.678"
        end="01:24:58.307"><span region="Default">♪ To kiss in cars and downtown bars ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:24:58.390"
        end="01:25:01.602"><span region="Default">♪ Was all we needed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:02.394"
        end="01:25:05.814"><span region="Default">♪ You drew stars around my scars ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:05.898"
        end="01:25:10.110"><span region="Default">♪ But now I'm bleeding ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:11.486"
        end="01:25:13.322"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I knew you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:13.405"
        end="01:25:17.159"><span region="Default">♪ Stepping on the last train<br/>Marked me like a bloodstain ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:17.242"
        end="01:25:18.911"><span region="Default">♪ I... ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:18.994"
        end="01:25:20.829"><span region="Default">♪ I knew you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:20.913"
        end="01:25:24.625"><span region="Default">♪ Tried to change the ending<br/>Peter losing Wendy ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:24.708"
        end="01:25:26.251"><span region="Default">♪ I... ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:26.335"
        end="01:25:28.045"><span region="Default">♪ I knew you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:28.128"
        end="01:25:31.965"><span region="Default">♪ Leaving like a father<br/>Running like water ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:32.049"
        end="01:25:33.383"><span region="Default">♪ I... ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:33.467"
        end="01:25:37.763"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause when you are young<br/>They assume you know nothing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:39.097"
        end="01:25:42.726"><span region="Default">♪ But I knew you'd linger<br/>Like a tattoo kiss ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:42.809"
        end="01:25:46.480"><span region="Default">♪ I knew you'd haunt all of my what-ifs ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:46.563"
        end="01:25:50.192"><span region="Default">♪ The smell of smoke<br/>Would hang around this long ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:50.275"
        end="01:25:53.904"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I knew everything<br/>When I was young ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:53.987"
        end="01:25:57.616"><span region="Default">♪ I knew I'd curse you<br/>For the longest time ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:25:57.699"
        end="01:26:01.245"><span region="Default">♪ Chasing shadows in the grocery line ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:01.328"
        end="01:26:04.915"><span region="Default">♪ I knew you'd miss me<br/>Once the thrill expired ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:04.998"
        end="01:26:08.335"><span region="Default">♪ And you'd be standing<br/>In my front porch light ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:08.418"
        end="01:26:11.755"><span region="Default">♪ And I knew you'd come back to me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:12.506"
        end="01:26:15.217"><span region="Default">♪ You'd come back to me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:16.051"
        end="01:26:18.887"><span region="Default">♪ And you'd come back to me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:19.805"
        end="01:26:21.765"><span region="Default">♪ And you'd come back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:25.227"
        end="01:26:29.731"><span region="Default">♪ And when I felt like<br/>I was an old cardigan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:29.815"
        end="01:26:31.733"><span region="Default">♪ Under someone's bed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:32.818"
        end="01:26:37.406"><span region="Default">♪ You put me on<br/>And said I was your favorite ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:39.408"
        end="01:26:40.409"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:55.966"
        end="01:26:59.178"><span region="Default">It's just, it's just crazy to think<br/>I'm about to sing, uh,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:26:59.261"
        end="01:27:02.181"><span region="Default">the last song I ever sang<br/>in the folklore cabin.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:02.264"
        end="01:27:03.348"><span region="Default">That's wild.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:03.932"
        end="01:27:06.852"><span region="Default">Oh, my God. [chuckles]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:08.353"
        end="01:27:11.315"><span region="Default">The folklore cabin<br/>that I'm currently standing in...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:11.398"
        end="01:27:13.192"><span region="Default">[♪ strumming guitar]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:13.275"
        end="01:27:15.027"><span region="Default">...that, uh, this, this whole thing</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:15.110"
        end="01:27:18.071"><span region="Default">kind of just originated<br/>in my imagination,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:18.155"
        end="01:27:20.866"><span region="Default">because the whole folklore album really</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:20.949"
        end="01:27:22.743"><span region="Default">was sort of like a figment<br/>of my imagination.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:22.826"
        end="01:27:27.623"><span region="Default">It was like this, um,<br/>this, this escape,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:27.706"
        end="01:27:30.459"><span region="Default">this pretend escape place in my mind,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:30.542"
        end="01:27:32.836"><span region="Default">um, where I would go every day<br/>and write songs.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:32.920"
        end="01:27:34.838"><span region="Default">And it really took my mind off of</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:34.922"
        end="01:27:37.466"><span region="Default">what was happening<br/>in the world at that time,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:37.549"
        end="01:27:40.761"><span region="Default">which is that, um,<br/>I started writing folklore</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:40.844"
        end="01:27:42.763"><span region="Default">about two days into the pandemic.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:42.846"
        end="01:27:46.391"><span region="Default">And so this was like a way for me to...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:47.434"
        end="01:27:48.644"><span region="Default">just get out of myself.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:48.727"
        end="01:27:51.605"><span region="Default">And really, what ended up happening<br/>was I made an album that,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:52.773"
        end="01:27:55.609"><span region="Default">it kind of forced me to tell stories<br/>in a different way.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:55.692"
        end="01:27:58.612"><span region="Default">Like, I have always tended to be a bit,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:27:58.695"
        end="01:28:01.865"><span region="Default">uh, uh, main-charactery in my songwriting,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:01.949"
        end="01:28:05.619"><span region="Default">like, I'll write from an autobiographical,<br/>personal place a lot of the time.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:05.702"
        end="01:28:07.120"><span region="Default">Don't know if you've ever noticed that?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:08.288"
        end="01:28:09.581"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:09.665"
        end="01:28:10.874"><span region="Default">but with folklore, I was like,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:10.958"
        end="01:28:15.337"><span region="Default">"You know what? I could, I could try to be<br/>more of a narrator this time</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:15.420"
        end="01:28:17.923"><span region="Default">"and, and I could try to,<br/>like, make up characters,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:18.006"
        end="01:28:21.009"><span region="Default">"and these characters fall in love<br/>and gets their, uh,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:21.093"
        end="01:28:24.930"><span region="Default">"get their hearts ripped out and have<br/>lots of drama between them."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:25.013"
        end="01:28:28.600"><span region="Default">And, uh, it's not, you know, I--<br/>I'm just the narrator.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:28.684"
        end="01:28:31.395"><span region="Default">I just work here, you know?<br/>I'm just telling you about it.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:31.478"
        end="01:28:34.648"><span region="Default">Uh, and so that's what I did.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:34.731"
        end="01:28:38.068"><span region="Default">And this is a story<br/>about a girl named Betty.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:39.027"
        end="01:28:40.821"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:40.904"
        end="01:28:43.156"><span region="Default">[♪ "betty" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:51.248"
        end="01:28:53.917"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, Betty, I won't make assumptions ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:54.001"
        end="01:28:56.378"><span region="Default">♪ About why you switched your homeroom ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:28:56.461"
        end="01:28:58.755"><span region="Default">♪ But I think it's 'cause of me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:01.425"
        end="01:29:05.179"><span region="Default">♪ Betty, one time, I was riding<br/>On my skateboard ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:05.262"
        end="01:29:09.224"><span region="Default">♪ When I passed your house<br/>It's like I couldn't breathe ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:11.101"
        end="01:29:15.898"><span region="Default">♪ You heard the rumors from Inez<br/>You can't believe a word she says ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:15.981"
        end="01:29:18.692"><span region="Default">♪ Most times, but this time, it was true ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:20.444"
        end="01:29:25.073"><span region="Default">♪ The worst thing that I ever did ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:25.157"
        end="01:29:29.369"><span region="Default">♪ Was what I did to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:32.372"
        end="01:29:35.209"><span region="Default">♪ But if I just showed up at your party ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:35.292"
        end="01:29:37.628"><span region="Default">♪ Would you have me?<br/>Would you want me? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:37.711"
        end="01:29:40.422"><span region="Default">♪ Would you tell me to go fuck myself ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:40.506"
        end="01:29:42.591"><span region="Default">♪ Or lead me to the garden? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:42.674"
        end="01:29:45.135"><span region="Default">♪ In the garden, would you trust me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:45.219"
        end="01:29:48.764"><span region="Default">♪ If I told you<br/>It was just a summer thing? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:48.847"
        end="01:29:52.309"><span region="Default">♪ I'm only seventeen<br/>I don't know anything ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:29:52.392"
        end="01:29:54.645"><span region="Default">♪ But I know I miss you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:03.904"
        end="01:30:07.282"><span region="Default">♪ I was walkin' home<br/>On broken cobblestones ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:07.366"
        end="01:30:10.327"><span region="Default">♪ Just thinkin' of you<br/>When she pulled up ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:10.410"
        end="01:30:13.247"><span region="Default">♪ Like a figment of my worst intentions ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:13.330"
        end="01:30:16.375"><span region="Default">♪ She said, "James, get in, let's drive" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:16.458"
        end="01:30:18.877"><span region="Default">♪ Those days turned into nights ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:18.961"
        end="01:30:20.462"><span region="Default">♪ Slept next to her ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:20.546"
        end="01:30:23.632"><span region="Default">♪ But I dreamt of you all summer long ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:36.311"
        end="01:30:38.939"><span region="Default">♪ Well, Betty, I'm here on your doorstep ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:39.022"
        end="01:30:41.441"><span region="Default">♪ And I planned it out for weeks now ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:41.525"
        end="01:30:43.986"><span region="Default">♪ But it's finally sinkin' in ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:46.321"
        end="01:30:48.907"><span region="Default">♪ Betty, right now is the last time ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:48.991"
        end="01:30:51.368"><span region="Default">♪ I can dream about what happens ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:51.451"
        end="01:30:53.996"><span region="Default">♪ When you see my face again ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:30:55.622"
        end="01:31:00.377"><span region="Default">♪ The only thing I wanna do ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:00.460"
        end="01:31:04.464"><span region="Default">♪ Is make it up to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:07.467"
        end="01:31:11.388"><span region="Default">♪ So I showed up at your party ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:11.471"
        end="01:31:14.641"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:17.686"
        end="01:31:21.440"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah, I showed up at your party ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:23.275"
        end="01:31:25.777"><span region="Default">[♪ music building]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:27.613"
        end="01:31:30.073"><span region="Default">♪ Yeah, I showed up at your party ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:30.157"
        end="01:31:32.659"><span region="Default">♪ Will you have me?<br/>Will you love me? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:32.743"
        end="01:31:34.828"><span region="Default">♪ Will you kiss me on the porch ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:34.912"
        end="01:31:37.748"><span region="Default">♪ In front of all your stupid friends? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:37.831"
        end="01:31:41.460"><span region="Default">♪ If you kiss me<br/>Will it be just like I dreamed it? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:41.543"
        end="01:31:43.504"><span region="Default">♪ Will it patch your broken wings? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:43.587"
        end="01:31:45.547"><span region="Default">♪ I'm only seventeen ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:45.631"
        end="01:31:47.341"><span region="Default">♪ I don't know anything ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:47.424"
        end="01:31:49.801"><span region="Default">♪ But I know I miss you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:52.054"
        end="01:31:54.806"><span region="Default">♪ Standing in your cardigan ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:31:57.309"
        end="01:31:59.770"><span region="Default">♪ Kissin' in my car again ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:00.979"
        end="01:32:04.858"><span region="Default">♪ Stopped at a streetlight<br/>You know I miss you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:07.819"
        end="01:32:10.030"><span region="Default">-[♪ song ends]<br/>-[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:23.460"
        end="01:32:25.337"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:31.760"
        end="01:32:33.595"><span region="Default">[♪ playing piano]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:51.822"
        end="01:32:54.533"><span region="Default">So, folklore actually has a sister album.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:32:55.075"
        end="01:32:59.204"><span region="Default">Um, and I'm also really proud of that one.<br/>It's called evermore.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:05.377"
        end="01:33:06.920"><span region="Default">And evermore, um...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:08.255"
        end="01:33:10.549"><span region="Default">You know,<br/>I call it folklore's sister album</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:10.632"
        end="01:33:13.760"><span region="Default">because I wrote this album<br/>just immediately after I wrote folklore.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:13.844"
        end="01:33:17.806"><span region="Default">There was just no stopping<br/>in between the two albums, um...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:18.432"
        end="01:33:21.143"><span region="Default">And it came out<br/>a couple of months after folklore.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:21.226"
        end="01:33:25.272"><span region="Default">And it was really kind of staying<br/>in a similar world of,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:25.355"
        end="01:33:27.608"><span region="Default">of storytelling and escaping.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:27.691"
        end="01:33:30.235"><span region="Default">And, when I play these songs</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:30.319"
        end="01:33:32.863"><span region="Default">from this point in my life,<br/>like, it really...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:34.198"
        end="01:33:35.866"><span region="Default">reminds me of this feeling I would have</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:35.949"
        end="01:33:38.660"><span region="Default">after I would finish a song<br/>that I was really proud of.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:39.578"
        end="01:33:41.663"><span region="Default">And the feeling I would have,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:41.747"
        end="01:33:44.750"><span region="Default">because if you remember<br/>where we were at that point,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:45.459"
        end="01:33:47.628"><span region="Default">we didn't know the future of concerts,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:47.711"
        end="01:33:50.422"><span region="Default">we didn't know if we were ever gonna get<br/>to do this again,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:50.506"
        end="01:33:52.549"><span region="Default">where we're all in the same room,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:52.633"
        end="01:33:55.427"><span region="Default">gloriously singing the same words<br/>at the same time</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:55.511"
        end="01:33:58.680"><span region="Default">and relating to each other and feeling<br/>like we've all been there before.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:33:58.764"
        end="01:34:00.182"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:04.561"
        end="01:34:09.650"><span region="Default">And so, uh, after I would finish a song<br/>and finish writing,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:09.733"
        end="01:34:12.528"><span region="Default">I would just think,<br/>"I wonder if I'm ever gonna get to...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:13.779"
        end="01:34:16.698"><span region="Default">sing 'champagne problems'<br/>in a sold-out stadium in Vancouver."</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:16.782"
        end="01:34:18.951"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:19.701"
        end="01:34:21.662"><span region="Default">[♪ "champagne problems" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:41.181"
        end="01:34:44.101"><span region="Default">♪ You booked the night train<br/>For a reason ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:45.102"
        end="01:34:48.814"><span region="Default">♪ So you could sit there in this hurt ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:51.441"
        end="01:34:55.195"><span region="Default">♪ Bustling crowds or silent sleepers ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:34:55.904"
        end="01:34:59.616"><span region="Default">♪ You're not sure which is worse ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:00.617"
        end="01:35:04.580"><span region="Default">♪ Because I dropped<br/>Your hand while dancing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:04.663"
        end="01:35:07.082"><span region="Default">♪ Left you out there standing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:07.165"
        end="01:35:09.543"><span region="Default">♪ Crestfallen on the landing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:09.626"
        end="01:35:12.504"><span region="Default">♪ Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:12.588"
        end="01:35:15.090"><span region="Default">♪ Your mom's ring in your pocket ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:15.174"
        end="01:35:17.759"><span region="Default">♪ My picture in your wallet ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:17.843"
        end="01:35:20.220"><span region="Default">♪ Your heart was glass, I dropped it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:20.304"
        end="01:35:22.848"><span region="Default">♪ Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:34.276"
        end="01:35:37.404"><span region="Default">♪ You told your family for a reason ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:38.822"
        end="01:35:42.159"><span region="Default">♪ You couldn't keep it in ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:44.536"
        end="01:35:47.873"><span region="Default">♪ Your sister splashed out on the bottle ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:49.082"
        end="01:35:53.337"><span region="Default">♪ Now no one's celebrating ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:55.088"
        end="01:35:57.674"><span region="Default">♪ Dom Pérignon, you brought it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:35:57.758"
        end="01:36:00.260"><span region="Default">♪ No crowd of friends applauded ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:00.344"
        end="01:36:02.888"><span region="Default">♪ Your hometown skeptics called it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:02.971"
        end="01:36:05.516"><span region="Default">♪ Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:05.599"
        end="01:36:08.227"><span region="Default">♪ You had a speech, you're speechless ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:08.310"
        end="01:36:10.812"><span region="Default">♪ Love slipped beyond your reaches ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:10.896"
        end="01:36:13.398"><span region="Default">♪ And I couldn't give a reason ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:13.482"
        end="01:36:16.026"><span region="Default">♪ Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:16.902"
        end="01:36:19.488"><span region="Default">[vocalizing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:27.329"
        end="01:36:29.998"><span region="Default">[vocalizing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:38.423"
        end="01:36:40.801"><span region="Default">♪ Your Midas touch on the Chevy door ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:40.884"
        end="01:36:43.428"><span region="Default">♪ November flush and your flannel cure ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:43.512"
        end="01:36:45.681"><span region="Default">♪ "This dorm was once a madhouse" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:45.764"
        end="01:36:48.141"><span region="Default">♪ I made a joke<br/>"Well, it's made for me" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:48.225"
        end="01:36:51.520"><span region="Default">♪ How evergreen our group of friends ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:51.603"
        end="01:36:54.189"><span region="Default">♪ Don't think we'll say that word again ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:54.273"
        end="01:36:57.526"><span region="Default">♪ And soon they'll have<br/>The nerve to deck the halls ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:57.609"
        end="01:36:59.069"><span region="Default">♪ That we once walked through ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:36:59.152"
        end="01:37:01.405"><span region="Default">♪ One for the money, two for the show ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:01.488"
        end="01:37:03.907"><span region="Default">♪ I never was ready, so I watch you go ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:03.991"
        end="01:37:06.743"><span region="Default">♪ Sometimes you just<br/>Don't know the answer ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:06.827"
        end="01:37:09.371"><span region="Default">♪ Till someone's on their knees<br/>And asks you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:09.454"
        end="01:37:11.874"><span region="Default">♪ "She would've made such a lovely bride ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:11.957"
        end="01:37:14.877"><span region="Default">♪ What a shame<br/>She's fucked in the head," they said ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:14.960"
        end="01:37:17.129"><span region="Default">♪ But you'll find the real thing instead ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:17.212"
        end="01:37:20.340"><span region="Default">♪ She'll patch up<br/>Your tapestry that I shred ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:20.924"
        end="01:37:23.051"><span region="Default">♪ Hold your hand while dancin' ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:23.594"
        end="01:37:25.888"><span region="Default">♪ Never leave you standing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:25.971"
        end="01:37:28.307"><span region="Default">♪ Crestfallen on the landing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:29.016"
        end="01:37:30.976"><span region="Default">♪ With champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:31.476"
        end="01:37:34.104"><span region="Default">♪ Your mom's ring in your pocket ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:34.188"
        end="01:37:36.899"><span region="Default">♪ Her picture in your wallet ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:36.982"
        end="01:37:41.987"><span region="Default">♪ You won't remember all my<br/>Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:44.615"
        end="01:37:46.909"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:37:47.826"
        end="01:37:52.789"><span region="Default">♪ You won't remember all my<br/>Champagne problems ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:11.308"
        end="01:38:14.770"><span region="Default">-[♪ song ends]<br/>-[audience cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:38:55.853"
        end="01:38:58.313"><span region="Default">[audience cheering louder]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:06.321"
        end="01:39:08.949"><span region="Default">Three, two, one.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:09.032"
        end="01:39:13.120"><span region="Default">♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:13.203"
        end="01:39:16.290"><span region="Default">♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:16.373"
        end="01:39:19.710"><span region="Default">♪ Happy birthday, dear Taylor ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:39:21.378"
        end="01:39:26.049"><span region="Default">♪ Happy birthday to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:31.615"
        end="01:40:33.242"><span region="Default">[mouthing] Oh, my God.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:46.380"
        end="01:40:48.799"><span region="Default">[audience cheering louder]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:40:54.805"
        end="01:40:56.056"><span region="Default">[mouthing] Oh, my God.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:09.152"
        end="01:41:14.032"><span region="Default">Thank you. Well, this tour has been<br/>the adventure of a lifetime.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:14.116"
        end="01:41:19.079"><span region="Default">And I speak on behalf of my band,<br/>my crew, my fellow performers,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:19.162"
        end="01:41:21.081"><span region="Default">who all left their families</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:21.164"
        end="01:41:24.626"><span region="Default">and have spent time away from everything<br/>that they know and love</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:24.710"
        end="01:41:29.882"><span region="Default">and have performed when they were sick,<br/>when anything was going on in their lives,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:29.965"
        end="01:41:32.634"><span region="Default">they made sure that this show<br/>happened for you.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:32.718"
        end="01:41:35.929"><span region="Default">And I just wanted to say<br/>that on behalf of all of us,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:36.013"
        end="01:41:38.974"><span region="Default">we will never forget<br/>you giving us that moment.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:39.057"
        end="01:41:41.310"><span region="Default">Thank you so much, Vancouver.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:41:41.393"
        end="01:41:43.228"><span region="Default">[audience cheering]</span></p>
