      <p
        begin="01:48:09.406"
        end="01:48:15.537"><span region="Default">♪ And if I'm dead to you<br/>Why are you at the wake? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:15.621"
        end="01:48:18.415"><span region="Default">♪ Cursing my name, wishing I stayed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:18.498"
        end="01:48:21.710"><span region="Default">♪ Look at how my tears ricochet ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:29.593"
        end="01:48:35.432"><span region="Default">♪ We gather stones<br/>Never knowing what they'll mean ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:37.184"
        end="01:48:43.273"><span region="Default">♪ Some to throw<br/>Some to make a diamond ring ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:43.357"
        end="01:48:47.528"><span region="Default">♪ You know I didn't want to<br/>Have to haunt you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:47.611"
        end="01:48:50.155"><span region="Default">♪ But what a ghostly scene ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:51.406"
        end="01:48:55.035"><span region="Default">♪ You wear the same jewels<br/>That I gave you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:48:55.118"
        end="01:48:57.996"><span region="Default">♪ As you bury me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:01.124"
        end="01:49:07.047"><span region="Default">♪ I didn't have it in myself<br/>To go with grace ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:08.298"
        end="01:49:14.888"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause when I'd fight<br/>You used to tell me I was brave ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:15.806"
        end="01:49:21.478"><span region="Default">♪ And if I'm dead to you<br/>Why are you at the wake? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:21.562"
        end="01:49:25.190"><span region="Default">♪ Cursing my name, wishing I stayed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:25.274"
        end="01:49:28.777"><span region="Default">♪ Look at how my tears ricochet ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:28.861"
        end="01:49:32.406"><span region="Default">♪ And I can go anywhere I want ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:32.489"
        end="01:49:36.368"><span region="Default">♪ Anywhere I want, just not home ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:36.451"
        end="01:49:39.663"><span region="Default">♪ And you can aim for my heart<br/>Go for blood ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:39.746"
        end="01:49:43.709"><span region="Default">♪ But you would still miss me<br/>In your bones ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:43.792"
        end="01:49:47.337"><span region="Default">♪ And I still talk to you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:47.421"
        end="01:49:50.924"><span region="Default">♪ When I'm screaming at the sky ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:51.008"
        end="01:49:54.553"><span region="Default">♪ And when you can't sleep at night ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:49:54.636"
        end="01:50:00.350"><span region="Default">♪ You hear my stolen lullabies ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:05.731"
        end="01:50:11.737"><span region="Default">♪ I didn't have it in myself<br/>To go with grace ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:13.197"
        end="01:50:19.411"><span region="Default">♪ And so the battleships will sink<br/>Beneath the waves ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:20.495"
        end="01:50:26.168"><span region="Default">♪ You had to kill me<br/>But it killed you just the same ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:26.251"
        end="01:50:29.588"><span region="Default">♪ Cursing my name, wishing I stayed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:29.671"
        end="01:50:33.050"><span region="Default">♪ You turned into your worst fears ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:33.133"
        end="01:50:37.179"><span region="Default">♪ And you're tossing out blame<br/>Drunk on this pain ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:37.262"
        end="01:50:39.389"><span region="Default">♪ Crossing out the good years ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:39.473"
        end="01:50:44.728"><span region="Default">♪ And you're cursing my name<br/>Wishing I stayed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="01:50:44.811"
        end="01:50:47.564"><span region="Default">♪ Look at how my tears ricochet ♪</span></p>
