        end="02:33:45.767"><span region="Default">[♪ "The Smallest Man<br/>Who Ever Lived" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:33:45.851"
        end="02:33:48.770"><span region="Default">♪ Was any of it true? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:33:51.565"
        end="02:33:55.903"><span region="Default">♪ Gazing at me starry-eyed ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:33:56.904"
        end="02:34:00.866"><span region="Default">♪ In your Jehovah's Witness suit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:03.577"
        end="02:34:07.915"><span region="Default">♪ Who the fuck was that guy? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:09.291"
        end="02:34:15.214"><span region="Default">♪ You tried to buy some pills ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:15.297"
        end="02:34:21.220"><span region="Default">♪ From a friend of friends of mine ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:21.303"
        end="02:34:24.806"><span region="Default">♪ They just ghosted you ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:27.100"
        end="02:34:31.605"><span region="Default">♪ Now you know what it feels like ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:33.857"
        end="02:34:36.151"><span region="Default">♪ And I don't even want you back ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:36.235"
        end="02:34:39.363"><span region="Default">♪ I just want to know ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:39.446"
        end="02:34:43.825"><span region="Default">♪ If rusting my sparkling summer<br/>was the goal ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:45.661"
        end="02:34:49.289"><span region="Default">♪ And I don't miss what we had,<br/>but could someone give ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:51.416"
        end="02:34:55.963"><span region="Default">♪ A message to the smallest man<br/>who ever lived? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:34:58.882"
        end="02:35:04.471"><span region="Default">♪ Were you sent by someone<br/>who wanted me dead? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:04.555"
        end="02:35:10.269"><span region="Default">♪ Did you sleep with a gun<br/>underneath our bed? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:10.978"
        end="02:35:17.526"><span region="Default">♪ Were you writin' a book?<br/>Were you a sleeper cell spy? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:17.609"
        end="02:35:22.322"><span region="Default">♪ In fifty years,<br/>will all this be declassified? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:22.406"
        end="02:35:26.451"><span region="Default">♪ And you'll confess why you did it ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:26.535"
        end="02:35:29.538"><span region="Default">♪ And I'll say, "Good riddance" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:29.621"
        end="02:35:34.543"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause it wasn't sexy<br/>once it wasn't forbidden ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:34.626"
        end="02:35:38.630"><span region="Default">♪ I would've died for your sins, instead ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:38.714"
        end="02:35:40.883"><span region="Default">♪ I just died inside ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:42.092"
        end="02:35:47.097"><span region="Default">♪ And you deserve prison,<br/>but you won't get time ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:47.181"
        end="02:35:51.018"><span region="Default">♪ You'll slide into inboxes ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:51.101"
        end="02:35:54.396"><span region="Default">♪ And slip through the bars ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:54.479"
        end="02:35:59.735"><span region="Default">♪ You crashed my party<br/>and your rental car ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:35:59.818"
        end="02:36:02.946"><span region="Default">♪ You said normal girls were boring ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:03.030"
        end="02:36:05.824"><span region="Default">♪ But you were gone by the morning ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:05.908"
        end="02:36:12.372"><span region="Default">♪ You kicked out the stage lights,<br/>but you're still performing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:12.456"
        end="02:36:15.542"><span region="Default">♪ And in plain sight, you hid ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:15.626"
        end="02:36:18.921"><span region="Default">♪ But you are what you did ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:19.004"
        end="02:36:24.051"><span region="Default">♪ And I'll forget you,<br/>but I'll never forgive ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:24.134"
        end="02:36:29.556"><span region="Default">♪ The smallest man who ever lived ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:30.432"
        end="02:36:32.434"><span region="Default">-[♪ song ends]<br/>-[crowd cheers]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:40.442"
        end="02:36:42.444"><span region="Default">[♪ upbeat pop music playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:36:43.237"
        end="02:36:45.239"><span region="Default">[imperceptible]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:37:05.050"
        end="02:37:09.680"><span region="Default">[♪ "I Can Do It With a Broken Heart<br/>(Broken Hearted Showgirl Version)" plays]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:37:09.763"
        end="02:37:11.849"><span region="Default">[imperceptible]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:37:22.484"
        end="02:37:26.321"><span region="Default">[♪ "I Can Do It With a Broken Heart<br/>(Broken Hearted Showgirl Version)" plays]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:37:32.578"
        end="02:37:34.580"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
