        begin="02:37:47.384"
        end="02:37:49.386"><span region="Default">[imperceptible]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:37:56.018"
        end="02:37:58.729"><span region="Default">[imperceptible]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:07.154"
        end="02:38:09.448"><span region="Default">[♪ "I Can Do It<br/>With A Broken Heart" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:15.204"
        end="02:38:19.374"><span region="Default">♪ I can read your mind ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:22.377"
        end="02:38:26.965"><span region="Default">♪ "She's having the time of her life" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:30.052"
        end="02:38:32.054"><span region="Default">♪ There in her glittering prime ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:32.137"
        end="02:38:37.309"><span region="Default">♪ The lights refract sequined stars<br/>off her silhouette every night ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:37.893"
        end="02:38:41.730"><span region="Default">♪ I can show you lies ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:41.813"
        end="02:38:43.857"><span region="Default">[man and crowd] ♪ One, two, three, four ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:43.941"
        end="02:38:47.945"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I'm a real tough kid,<br/>I can handle my shit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:48.028"
        end="02:38:50.948"><span region="Default">♪ They said, "Babe,<br/>you gotta fake it till you make it" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:51.031"
        end="02:38:55.327"><span region="Default">♪ And I did Lights, camera, bitch smile,<br/>even when you wanna die ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:55.410"
        end="02:38:59.373"><span region="Default">♪ He said he'd love me all his life ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:38:59.456"
        end="02:39:00.749"><span region="Default">♪ But that life was too short ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:00.832"
        end="02:39:02.835"><span region="Default">♪ Breaking down, I hit the floor ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:02.918"
        end="02:39:06.421"><span region="Default">♪ All the pieces of me shattered<br/>as the crowd was chanting "More" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:06.505"
        end="02:39:10.676"><span region="Default">♪ I was grinning like I'm winning,<br/>I was hitting my marks ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:10.759"
        end="02:39:14.263"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I can do it with a broken heart ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:15.889"
        end="02:39:21.687"><span region="Default">♪ I'm so depressed,<br/>I act like it's my birthday every day ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:23.230"
        end="02:39:28.861"><span region="Default">♪ I'm so obsessed with him<br/>but he avoids me like the plague ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:30.696"
        end="02:39:36.243"><span region="Default">♪ I cry a lot but I am so productive,<br/>it's an art ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:38.161"
        end="02:39:43.667"><span region="Default">♪ You know you're good when you can even<br/>do it with a broken heart ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:43.750"
        end="02:39:48.463"><span region="Default">♪ I can hold my breath ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:51.258"
        end="02:39:53.844"><span region="Default">♪ I've been doing it since ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:53.927"
        end="02:39:55.846"><span region="Default">♪ He left ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:39:57.973"
        end="02:40:00.851"><span region="Default">♪ I keep finding<br/>his things in drawers ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:00.934"
        end="02:40:05.105"><span region="Default">♪ Crucial evidence,<br/>I didn't imagine the whole thing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:05.189"
        end="02:40:09.443"><span region="Default">♪ I'm sure I can pass this test ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:10.611"
        end="02:40:12.362"><span region="Default">♪ One, two, three, four ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:12.446"
        end="02:40:16.408"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I'm a real tough kid,<br/>I can handle my shit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:16.491"
        end="02:40:19.286"><span region="Default">♪ They said, "Babe,<br/>you gotta fake it till you make it" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:19.369"
        end="02:40:21.997"><span region="Default">♪ And I did<br/>Lights, camera, bitch smile ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:22.080"
        end="02:40:23.916"><span region="Default">♪ In stilettos for miles ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:23.999"
        end="02:40:27.628"><span region="Default">♪ He said he'd love me for all time ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:27.711"
        end="02:40:29.505"><span region="Default">♪ But that time was quite short ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:29.588"
        end="02:40:31.340"><span region="Default">♪ Breaking down, I hit the floor ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:31.423"
        end="02:40:35.135"><span region="Default">♪ All the pieces of me shattered<br/>as the crowd was chanting "More" ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:35.219"
        end="02:40:39.139"><span region="Default">♪ I was grinning like I'm winning,<br/>I was hitting my marks ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:39.223"
        end="02:40:42.643"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I can do it<br/>with a broken heart ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:44.561"
        end="02:40:50.067"><span region="Default">♪ I'm so depressed,<br/>I act like it's my birthday every day ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:51.276"
        end="02:40:57.366"><span region="Default">♪ I'm so obsessed with him<br/>but he avoids me like the plague ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:40:59.368"
        end="02:41:04.998"><span region="Default">♪ I cry a lot but I am so productive,<br/>it's an art ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:06.416"
        end="02:41:12.297"><span region="Default">♪ You know you're good when you can even<br/>do it with a broken heart ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:14.174"
        end="02:41:19.596"><span region="Default">♪ You know you're good when you can even<br/>do it with a broken heart ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:21.515"
        end="02:41:24.726"><span region="Default">♪ You know you're good ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:25.811"
        end="02:41:26.812"><span region="Default">I'm good.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:28.647"
        end="02:41:30.357"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:30.440"
        end="02:41:32.985"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause I'm miserable ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:33.068"
        end="02:41:35.445"><span region="Default">♪ And nobody even knows ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:37.322"
        end="02:41:40.784"><span region="Default">♪ Try and come for my job ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:41:40.951"
        end="02:41:43.662"><span region="Default">-[♪ song ends]<br/>-[crowd cheers]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:17.196"
        end="02:42:21.617"><span region="Default">Vancouver, welcome to the very last<br/>acoustic section of The Eras Tour.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:26.830"
        end="02:42:31.585"><span region="Default">The acoustic section is something<br/>that, um, I started, um...</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:31.668"
        end="02:42:33.670"><span region="Default">I came up with this tradition<br/>on The Eras Tour</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:33.754"
        end="02:42:36.215"><span region="Default">because it was really meant to,<br/>like, challenge me</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:36.298"
        end="02:42:39.009"><span region="Default">to perform lots<br/>and lots of different songs</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:39.092"
        end="02:42:41.261"><span region="Default">from different eras, different albums,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:41.345"
        end="02:42:43.639"><span region="Default">and, um, just try to,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:43.722"
        end="02:42:46.600"><span region="Default">you know, kind of play a guessing game<br/>every single night</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:46.683"
        end="02:42:48.977"><span region="Default">and think about what you might wanna hear.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:49.061"
        end="02:42:51.438"><span region="Default">And, uh, so every single night,<br/>it's different.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:51.522"
        end="02:42:54.775"><span region="Default">I'll do something on guitar,<br/>then I do something else on piano.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:54.858"
        end="02:42:57.819"><span region="Default">And, um, I was thinking about it,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:42:57.903"
        end="02:43:02.115"><span region="Default">because we've had<br/>so long to prepare for the,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:02.199"
        end="02:43:05.077"><span region="Default">the end of this tour, and, um,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:05.160"
        end="02:43:07.329"><span region="Default">so I was trying to think about what,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:08.664"
        end="02:43:12.125"><span region="Default">what songs really encapsulate<br/>how I feel about tonight.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:12.209"
        end="02:43:15.087"><span region="Default">And so I decided to go back to<br/>the beginning.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:15.170"
        end="02:43:19.174"><span region="Default">[♪ "A Place In This World" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:19.258"
        end="02:43:24.137"><span region="Default">♪ I don't know what I want<br/>So don't ask me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:24.221"
        end="02:43:27.641"><span region="Default">♪ Cause I'm still trying<br/>to figure it out ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:27.724"
        end="02:43:30.644"><span region="Default">♪ Don't know what's down this road ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:30.727"
        end="02:43:32.646"><span region="Default">♪ I'm just walking ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:32.729"
        end="02:43:36.483"><span region="Default">♪ Trying to see<br/>through the rain coming down ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:37.234"
        end="02:43:41.446"><span region="Default">♪ Even though I'm not the only one ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:41.530"
        end="02:43:45.367"><span region="Default">♪ Who feels the way I do ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:45.450"
        end="02:43:49.413"><span region="Default">♪ I'm alone, on my own ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:49.496"
        end="02:43:53.792"><span region="Default">♪ And that's all I know ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:53.876"
        end="02:43:57.921"><span region="Default">♪ I'll be strong, I'll be wrong ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:43:58.005"
        end="02:44:01.633"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, but life goes on ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:01.717"
        end="02:44:05.179"><span region="Default">♪ Oh, I'm just a girl ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:05.262"
        end="02:44:09.308"><span region="Default">♪ Trying to find a place in this world ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:09.391"
        end="02:44:11.393"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:11.476"
        end="02:44:13.478"><span region="Default">[♪ strumming mellow tune]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:38.462"
        end="02:44:40.255"><span region="Default">-[♪ "New Romantics" playing]<br/>-♪ We're all bored ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:40.339"
        end="02:44:42.090"><span region="Default">♪ We're all so tired of everything ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:42.174"
        end="02:44:45.761"><span region="Default">♪ We wait for trains<br/>that just aren't coming ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:45.844"
        end="02:44:49.556"><span region="Default">♪ We show off<br/>our different scarlet letters ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:50.307"
        end="02:44:52.601"><span region="Default">♪Trust me, mine is better ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:54.019"
        end="02:44:55.896"><span region="Default">♪ We're so young ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:55.979"
        end="02:44:57.606"><span region="Default">♪ But we're on the road to ruin ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:44:57.689"
        end="02:45:02.194"><span region="Default">♪ We play dumb,<br/>we know exactly what we're doin' ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:02.277"
        end="02:45:05.739"><span region="Default">♪ We cry tears of mascara<br/>in the bathroom ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:05.822"
        end="02:45:08.408"><span region="Default">♪ Honey, life is just a classroom ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:08.492"
        end="02:45:11.370"><span region="Default">♪ Ah-ah-ah-ah-ah-ah ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:11.453"
        end="02:45:15.374"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause baby, I could build a castle ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:15.457"
        end="02:45:18.836"><span region="Default">♪ Out of all the bricks they threw at me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:18.919"
        end="02:45:22.798"><span region="Default">♪ And every day is like a battle ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:22.881"
        end="02:45:26.510"><span region="Default">♪ But every night with us<br/>is like a dream ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:26.593"
        end="02:45:28.470"><span region="Default">♪ Baby, we're the new romantics ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:28.554"
        end="02:45:30.222"><span region="Default">♪ Come on, come along with me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:30.305"
        end="02:45:31.640"><span region="Default">♪ Heartbreak is the national anthem ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:31.723"
        end="02:45:35.978"><span region="Default">♪ We sing it proudly<br/>We are too busy dancing ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:36.061"
        end="02:45:38.313"><span region="Default">♪ To get knocked off our feet ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:38.397"
        end="02:45:40.023"><span region="Default">♪ Baby, we're the new romantics ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:40.107"
        end="02:45:43.652"><span region="Default">♪ The best people in life are free ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:47.990"
        end="02:45:51.869"><span region="Default">♪ So, come on, come along<br/>with me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:45:57.791"
        end="02:46:02.296"><span region="Default">♪ And maybe I'm just a girl on a mission ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:46:02.379"
        end="02:46:07.759"><span region="Default">♪ But I'm ready to fly ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:46:07.843"
        end="02:46:12.264"><span region="Default">♪ So please take my hand ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:46:12.347"
        end="02:46:16.602"><span region="Default">♪ And please take me dancing, and ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="02:46:16.685"
        end="02:46:19.271"><span region="Default">♪ Please leave me stranded ♪</span></p>
      <p
