      <p
        begin="03:14:56.446"
        end="03:15:00.534"><span region="Default">♪ I've been scheming<br/>Like a criminal ever since ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:15:00.617"
        end="03:15:03.954"><span region="Default">♪ To make them love me<br/>And make it seem effortless ♪</span></p>
