      <p
        begin="03:18:08.222"
        end="03:18:10.974"><span region="Default">♪ Purring in my lap 'cause it loves me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:11.058"
        end="03:18:13.519"><span region="Default">♪ Flexing like a goddamn acrobat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:13.602"
        end="03:18:15.646"><span region="Default">♪ Me and karma vibe like that ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:16.271"
        end="03:18:18.857"><span region="Default">♪ Ask me what I learned<br/>from all those years ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:18.941"
        end="03:18:21.443"><span region="Default">♪ Ask me what I earned<br/>from all those tears ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:21.527"
        end="03:18:28.492"><span region="Default">♪ Ask me why so many fade,<br/>but I'm still here ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:28.951"
        end="03:18:32.329"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause karma is the thunder<br/>Rattling your ground ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:32.412"
        end="03:18:35.374"><span region="Default">♪ Karma's on your scent<br/>like a bounty hunter ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:35.457"
        end="03:18:40.170"><span region="Default">♪ Karma's gonna track you down<br/>Step by step from town to town ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:40.254"
        end="03:18:43.006"><span region="Default">♪ Sweet like justice, karma is a queen ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:43.090"
        end="03:18:46.093"><span region="Default">♪ Karma takes all my friends<br/>to the summit ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:46.176"
        end="03:18:48.303"><span region="Default">♪ Karma is the guy on the Chiefs ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:48.387"
        end="03:18:50.430"><span region="Default">-♪ Coming straight home to me ♪<br/>-[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:50.514"
        end="03:18:53.767"><span region="Default">♪ 'Cause karma is my boyfriend<br/>Karma is a god ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:53.851"
        end="03:18:56.937"><span region="Default">♪ Karma is the breeze in my hair<br/>on the weekend ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:57.020"
        end="03:18:58.939"><span region="Default">♪ Karma's a relaxing thought ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:18:59.022"
        end="03:19:01.316"><span region="Default">♪ Aren't you envious<br/>that for you it's not? ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:01.400"
        end="03:19:04.152"><span region="Default">♪ Sweet like honey, karma is a cat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:04.236"
        end="03:19:06.655"><span region="Default">♪ Purring in my lap 'cause it loves me ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:06.738"
        end="03:19:09.283"><span region="Default">♪ Flexing like a goddamn acrobat ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:09.366"
        end="03:19:12.119"><span region="Default">♪ Me and karma vibe like that ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:13.662"
        end="03:19:16.248"><span region="Default">♪ Karma is my boyfriend ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:16.331"
        end="03:19:18.584"><span region="Default">♪ Karma is a god ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:20.294"
        end="03:19:23.046"><span region="Default">♪ Mm-hmm ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:24.298"
        end="03:19:29.178"><span region="Default">♪ Karma's a relaxing thought ♪</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:32.806"
        end="03:19:36.226"><span region="Default">Vancouver, I love you so very much.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:37.144"
        end="03:19:40.397"><span region="Default">Thank you for giving us<br/>absolutely everything you had tonight.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:40.939"
        end="03:19:43.859"><span region="Default">But will you please treat<br/>these amazing dancers</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:43.942"
        end="03:19:47.154"><span region="Default">to the loudest applause<br/>they have heard on the tour yet?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:47.237"
        end="03:19:49.990"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering loudly]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:19:50.073"
        end="03:19:52.201"><span region="Default">[♪ "Karma" continues playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:05.714"
        end="03:20:08.717"><span region="Default">And now, as they take their final bow,</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:08.800"
        end="03:20:12.095"><span region="Default">will you please make<br/>the most amount of noise possible</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:12.179"
        end="03:20:14.765"><span region="Default">for my extraordinary backing vocalists?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:15.724"
        end="03:20:17.476"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering loudly]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:25.234"
        end="03:20:28.320"><span region="Default">Vancouver, will you direct your attention<br/>to the main stage</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:29.780"
        end="03:20:33.909"><span region="Default">and make the most amount of love possible<br/>and give all your love</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:34.826"
        end="03:20:37.955"><span region="Default">to the most magnificent band<br/>in all the land?</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:38.789"
        end="03:20:40.415"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering loudly]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:48.966"
        end="03:20:50.175"><span region="Default">[mouthing] Oh, my God.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:51.593"
        end="03:20:52.761"><span region="Default">[mouthing] Oh, my God.</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:54.179"
        end="03:20:58.225"><span region="Default">[♪ emotional instrumental outro<br/>to "Karma" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:20:58.308"
        end="03:21:00.269"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:22:33.320"
        end="03:22:35.739"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering loudly]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:22:44.039"
        end="03:22:45.624"><span region="Default">[♪ song ends]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:22:45.707"
        end="03:22:47.459"><span region="Default">[cheering continues]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:23:32.713"
        end="03:23:35.716"><span region="Default">[♪ "I Can Do It With a Broken Heart<br/>(Instrumental)" playing]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:25:10.519"
        end="03:25:12.187"><span region="Default">[crowd cheering]</span></p>
      <p
        begin="03:26:59.628"
        end="03:27:00.629"><span region="Default">[♪ music ends]</span></p>
